    • Method Detail

      • cheatingChained

        public static CheatingByChained cheatingChained​(org.openqa.selenium.By... bys)
        When looking for only one item, cheats by only looking for one item at each level.

        Useful only if you want the first result of each By operation, otherwise use fasterChained(By...) or ByChained.

      • fasterChained

        public static FasterByChained fasterChained​(org.openqa.selenium.By... bys)
        When looking for only one item, speeds up the last By in the chain by only running it until it finds something.

        When using SearchContext.findElements(By), uses ByChained to find all possible elements as normal.

        Using this should be functionally equivalent to using ByChained, except faster in some cases.
